----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Test case name:  TC_L30SW_QT_36645860: Verify Invalid Operations without running reset Scenerio 2
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:   Verify the software shall be configured for an invalid operation caused by a direct FLOAT to fixed-point conversion operation or any other conversion operation to a fixed-point value (e.g., ceiling, floor, round, truncate, etc.) that results in a floating-point operation exception, the result shall be modified or limited.

